      description "List of used DNS server addresses. IPv4 address is specified in dotted quad notation, for example 130.100.92.154. RFC 791 describes syntax details. IPv6 address is specified by 8 groups of 16 bit hexadecimal values separated by colons, for example 2001:0db8:85a3:0000:0000:8a2e:0370:7334. RFC 4291 describes syntax details..";
